OL,3,CFermain cafe should never have been
OL,4,Csold to the States, family claim
OL,6,FA Guernsey beach cafe that has been at
OL,7,Fthe centre of a long-running tenancy
OL,8,Fdispute is now subject to questions
OL,9,Fover the land ownership itself.
OL,11,FDescendants of the late Percy Ferguson
OL,12,F- who owned the cafe until 2002 - say
OL,13,Fthe sale to Guernsey's government was
OL,14,Frushed through by a now deceased
OL,15,Fformer States Deputy who had Power of
OL,16,FAttorney over his assets.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
