OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779282675
OL,3,CFermain cafe should never have been
OL,4,Csold to the States, family claim
OL,6,FThe popular cafe has been subject to
OL,7,Fpublic controversy over the past
OL,8,Fcouple of years, after the current
OL,9,Ftenants objected to the States of
OL,10,FGuernsey announcing its intention to
OL,11,Fgive the tender to someone else.
OL,13,FThat disagreement has now been
OL,14,Fresolved, and Belmiro de Freitas and
OL,15,FManuela Walter will continue to run
OL,16,Fthe cafe until October 2028.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779282675
OL,3,CFermain cafe should never have been
OL,4,Csold to the States, family claim
OL,6,FHowever, the high-profile dispute
OL,7,Fsparked the interest of Percy's
OL,8,Fdescendants, who believe their
OL,9,Ffamily's wishes were dismissed by the
OL,10,FStates 24 years ago.
OL,12,FPercy was a descendant of the Mallett
OL,13,Ffamily, who had owned the land in
OL,14,FFermain since the 1800s.
OL,16,FPercy's will stated his intention to
OL,17,Fleave the cafe to his nephew, Horace
OL,18,FMallett.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779282675
OL,3,CFermain cafe should never have been
OL,4,Csold to the States, family claim
OL,6,FHowever, Horace died first and the
OL,7,Fcafe was sold to the States for
OL,8,F#70,000 five weeks before Percy passed
OL,9,Faway, by a sitting Deputy who had the
OL,10,FPower of Attorney over Percy's affairs.
OL,12,FPaperwork shows the site was valued at
OL,13,F#120,000 at the time of sale.
OL,15,FOne of Percy's descendants, James
OL,16,FWillcocks, believes "there appears to
OL,17,Fbe a clear conflict of interest in the
OL,18,Fsale of the cafe in 2002".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779282675
OL,3,CFermain cafe should never have been
OL,4,Csold to the States, family claim
OL,6,FHe explains: "The person who had the
OL,7,FPower of Attorney at that time was a
OL,8,Fsitting States member and was
OL,9,Fbrokering the deal as the executor to
OL,10,Fthe States of Guernsey, who they
OL,11,Fworked for.
OL,13,F"It certainly raises more questions
OL,14,Fthan it answers."
OL,16,FAnother family member, Gary Willcocks,
OL,17,Fagrees, stating that because Percy was
OL,18,Fnot of sound mind when the sale was
OL,19,Fmade, it should not have been dealt
OL,20,Fwith under Power of Attorney.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779282675
OL,3,CFermain cafe should never have been
OL,4,Csold to the States, family claim
OL,6,FHe adds: "My belief is if this were to
OL,7,Fbe sold, it would have needed a proper
OL,8,Fcourt guardianship."
OL,10,FHowever, it is a legally complicated
OL,11,Fsituation.
OL,13,FGuernsey Advocate Dr Raymond Ashton
OL,14,Fsaid that unless Percy's will
OL,15,Fexplicitly stated the cafe was to be
OL,16,Fleft to Horace and his beneficiaries,
OL,17,Fthe sale would not have been illegal.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779282675
OL,3,CFermain cafe should never have been
OL,4,Csold to the States, family claim
OL,6,FHe explains: "If it's left to a Mr
OL,7,FBloggs or Miss Bloggs - if it doesn't
OL,8,Fsay 'and heirs' - then there's no
OL,9,Fcomeback.
OL,11,F"The only reservation I think on that
OL,12,Fis if you are able to show the
OL,13,Ftestator meant not only who he's
OL,14,Fwilled it to but the heirs, so in
OL,15,Fother words, there's a mistake in the
OL,16,Fwill."
OL,18,FThe States of Guernsey say their
OL,19,Fpurchase was legal and fair.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
