OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779282675
OL,3,CFermain cafe should never have been
OL,4,Csold to the States, family claim
OL,6,FIn a statement, they explain: "It's
OL,7,Fevident that, as often happens in
OL,8,FGuernsey - especially in a
OL,9,Frelationship that lasted for decades -
OL,10,Fsome elements may have been handled a
OL,11,Flittle informally.
OL,13,F"That's not unusual, and nor does it
OL,14,Fsuggest anything inappropriate, but it
OL,15,Fdoes help explain why there might be
OL,16,Fcertain gaps within the documentation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1779282675
OL,3,CFermain cafe should never have been
OL,4,Csold to the States, family claim
OL,6,F"However, given all the work done at
OL,7,Fthe time - and more recently to look
OL,8,Fover 175 years of documentation - we
OL,9,Fare satisfied that there is no
OL,10,Fquestion today around ownership."
OL,12,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,13,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,14,FChannel's Jess Dunsdon and Luke
OL,15,FKeohane break down the key election
OL,16,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,17,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,18,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,19,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,20,FThursday...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/9
